        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Lastly at 3rd level, you gain the following Channel the Force option.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<h4>TELEKINETIC SLASH</h4>\n<p>When you deal damage with an at-will force power that requires a force attack or a saving throw, you can expend a use of your Channel the Force and expend force points to deal additional damage to the target, which is the same type as the power&rsquo;s damage. The additional damage is 1d8 for each point spent in this way.</p>\n<p>You can&rsquo;t deal more additional damage than the amount shown in the Focused Strikes column of the guardian table.</p>\n</blockquote>",
